                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>Changes to These Terms</h2>
                <p>
                    We reserve the right to modify these Terms of Service at any
                    time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated
                    date. Continued use of our services after changes
                    constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>Contact</h2>
                <p>
                    If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, you
                    can reach us at <a href="mailto:jan@lauscode.com">jan@lauscode.com</a>.
                </p>
            </section>
        </article>
